room_title: Escape room "WinterKeep" by Outside the Box Escape Room in Harrisburg
room_description: Welcome to beautiful WinterKeep, you've gathered here in the war room because hordes of evil winter walkers threaten invasion over the great wall. The cry, “Winter is coming”, has gone out! Your only hope to preserve the domain is to rally your bannermen to defend the kingdom, locate the six sigil objects, and secure your most powerful weapon of defense - a dragon's egg!
